snippet.title: DIAMOND CLASS 10 FULL GRAMMAR REVISION | MODALS/TENSES/VOICE/NARRATION/ERROR DETECTION/DETERMINERS
snippet.description:
CLASS 10 COMPLETE GRAMMAR REVISION IN ONE VIDEO | MODALS | TENSES | VOICE | NARRATION | ERROR DETECTION | DETERMINERS

Are you struggling with Class 10 English grammar and looking for a quick yet effective revision? This Complete Grammar Revision One Shot is all you need! Covering essential topics like modals, tenses, active and passive voice, narration (reported speech), error detection, and determiners, this video will make your preparation easier and more efficient.

🔍 What You’ll Learn:

✔️ Modals explained with real examples to enhance your understanding.
✔️ Tenses broken down clearly to eliminate confusion.
✔️ Active & Passive Voice conversion made simple.
✔️ Narration (Reported Speech) techniques to master direct and indirect speech.
✔️ Error Detection strategies to tackle tricky questions.
✔️ Determiners usage rules to strengthen your grammar.

🎯 Why You Should Watch This Video:

This video is designed for Class 10 students aiming to score full marks in the grammar section. Whether you’re revising for board exams or just want to sharpen your grammar skills, this one-shot revision will make even complex topics easy to grasp.

🌟 Key Features:

✅ Step-by-step explanations with high-scoring examples.
✅ Exam-focused strategies to help you avoid common mistakes.
✅ Solved practice questions for better retention.
✅ Simple and structured format for quick revision.

📚 Who Should Watch?

📌 Class 10 students preparing for board exams.
📌 Students needing a quick and effective grammar revision.
📌 Anyone looking to master fundamental grammar rules.

📌 Don’t Forget to Subscribe!
Hit the subscribe button for more Class 10 English Grammar tutorials and boost your exam preparation!

📢 Share this video with your classmates and help them ace their exams.
💬 Drop a comment if you have any questions or topics you’d like us to cover. Happy learning! 🚀

snippet.title: 🤣VJ Siddhu Speech Harshath Khan Speech Dragon Pre Release Event
snippet.description:
Dragon is an 2025 Indian Tamil-language film written and directed by Ashwath Marimuthu, from a story he co-wrote with Pradeep Ranganathan, and produced by AGS Entertainment. The film stars Pradeep in the titular role, alongside Anupama Parameswaran, Kayadu Lohar, George Maryan, Indumathy Manikandan, K. S. Ravikumar, Gautham Vasudev Menon, Mysskin, VJ Siddhu and Harshath Khan. The film has music composed by Leon James, cinematography handled by Niketh Bommi and editing by Pradeep E. Ragav. Dragon is scheduled to be released worldwide on 21 February 2025 in theatres. Dragon movie fdfs public review will be out on Feb 21st 2025. Dragon pre release event happened in chennai today. ne.description:
https://youtu.be/3uKsaGRK3yw

बाँकी रहेका ५०० जनाले, हामीले आफैँ बनाएको अति भव्य शहरमा बसिरहनका लागि प्रतिस्पर्धा गर्नु पर्नेछ (ठट्टा गरेको हैन)। एपिसोडको अन्त्य त आजसम्मै टिभीमा कहींकतै नभएको किसिमको 'रोचक' छ। अहिल्यै हेरी हाल्नुहोस् है!

ta.title: பீஸ்ட் கேம்ஸ் | எபிசொட் 2 (முழு அத்தியாயம்)
ta.description:
முதல் 3 எபிசோட்களை இங்கே இடுகையிட அனுமதிப்பதற்காக அமேசானிடம் எப்படியோ பேசினேன்… ஆனால் மீதமுள்ளவை பிரைம் வீடியோவில் மட்டுமே உள்ளன. இப்போது சென்று பாருங்கள்! https://unfur.ly/BeastGames

பீஸ்ட் கேம்ஸ் கிரெடிட்ஸ்: https://youtu.be/5xSirFgIPOM

pa.title: ਬੀਸਟ ਗੇਮਜ਼ | ਐਪਿਸੋਡ 2 (ਫੁਲ ਐਪਿਸੋਡ)
pa.description:
ਮੈਂ ਕਿਸੇ ਤਰੀਕੇ ਨਾਲ ਐਮਾਜ਼ੌਨ ਨੂੰ ਪਹਿਲੇ 3 ਐਪੀਸੋਡ ਇੱਥੇ ਪੋਸਟ ਕਰਨ ਦੇਣ ਲਈ ਮਨਾ ਲਿਆ … ਪਰ ਬਾਕੀ ਸਿਰਫ ਪ੍ਰਾਈਮ ਵੀਡੀਓ 'ਤੇ ਹਨ। ਹੁਣੇ ਜਾਓ ਤੇ ਵੇਖੋ! https://unfur.ly/BeastGames

ਬੀਸਟ ਗੇਮਜ਼ ਕਰੈਡਿਟਸ: https://youtu.be/5xSirFgIPOM

zh-Hant.title: 500人被困在了我的城市之中
zh-Hant.description:
https://youtu.be/3uKsaGRK3yw

剩下的500名參賽者需要為能夠留在我從零開始精心建造的龐大城市而拼搏（可不是跟你開玩笑呢）。這一集的結尾或許會是電視歷史上最為瘋狂的事情呢。誠邀你現在就來觀看！

ml.title: ബീസ്റ്റ് ഗെയിംസ് | എപ്പിസോഡ് 2 (ഫുൾ എപ്പിസോഡ്)
ml.description:
ആദ്യത്തെ മൂന്ന് എപ്പിസോഡ് പോസ്റ്റ് ചെയ്യാൻ ഞാൻ ആമസോണിനെ സമ്മതിപ്പിച്ചെടുത്തു....പക്ഷെ ബാക്കിയുള്ളതൊക്കെ  ഒൺലി ഓൺ പ്രൈം വീഡിയോ. ഇപ്പോൾ തന്നെ കാണൂ!  https://unfur.ly/BeastGames

ബീസ്റ്റ് ഗെയിംസ് ക്രെഡിറ്റ്സ് : https://youtu.be/5xSirFgIPOM

nl.title: 500 Mensen Zitten Vast In Mijn Stad
nl.description:
https://youtu.be/3uKsaGRK3yw

De overgebleven 500 deelnemers moeten strijden om te blijven in de GIGANTISCHE stad die ik helemaal vanaf de grond heb opgebouwd (geen grap). Het einde van de aflevering is misschien wel het meest bizarre dat ooit op televisie is gebeurd. Kijk nu!

pl.title: Beast Games | Odcinek 2 (Pełny Odcinek)
pl.description:
W jakiś sposób namówiłem Amazon, aby pozwolił mi opublikować tutaj pierwsze 3 odcinki... ale reszta jest TYLKO na Prime Video. Oglądaj teraz! https://unfur.ly/BeastGames

Źródło Beast Games: https://youtu.be/5xSirFgIPOM

es-ES.title: 500 personas atrapadas en mi ciudad
es-ES.description:
https://youtu.be/3uKsaGRK3yw

Los 500 concursantes que quedan deben luchar para permanecer en la GIGANTESCA ciudad que he construido de la nada (va en serio). El final del episodio es lo más delirante que ha ocurrido en la historia de la televisión. ¡Tienes que verlo!

no.title: 500 stykker er fanget i byen min
no.description:
https://youtu.be/3uKsaGRK3yw

De gjenværende 500 deltakerne må kjempe for å bli værende i KJEMPEBYEN jeg bygde fra bunnen av (Jeg tuller ikke). Slutten på episoden kan være det sprøeste som noensinne har skjedd i TV-historien. 
Sjekk den ut nå!

de.title: Beast Games | Episode 2 (Ganze Folge)
de.description:
Ich habe Amazon irgendwie überredet, mir zu erlauben, die ersten 3 Episoden hier zu posten... aber der Rest ist NUR auf Prime Video. Schau es dir jetzt an! https://unfur.ly/BeastGames

Credits: https://youtu.be/5xSirFgIPOM

fi.title: 500 ihmistä on loukussa kaupungissani
fi.description:
https://youtu.be/3uKsaGRK3yw

Loput 500 kilpailijaa joutuvat taistelemaan pysyäkseen MASSIIVISESSA kaupungissa, jonka rakensin tyhjästä (en vitsaile). Jakson loppu saattaa olla hulluinta, mitä television historiassa on koskaan tapahtunut. Katso se heti!

ur.title: میرے شہر میں 500 لوگ پھنسے ہوئے ہیں
ur.description:
https://youtu.be/3uKsaGRK3yw

باقی 500 شرکاء کو اس عظیم الشان شہر میں رہنے کیلئے مزید لڑنا ہوگا اور سچی بات بتاؤں کہ یہ شہر میں نے مکمل طور پر ہم نے بنایا ہے۔ اس قسط کا اختتام ایک ایسے پاگل پن پر ہوگا جو ٹی وی کی تاریخ میں کبھی نہیں ہوا۔ ابھی ملاحظہ کریں!

ca.title: 500 persones atrapades a la meva ciutat
ca.description:
https://youtu.be/3uKsaGRK3yw
Els 500 concursants restants han de lluitar per seguir a la immensa ciutat que he construït des de zero (no és broma). El final de l'episodi possiblement sigui la bogeria més gran que s'hagi vist mai a la televisió. Mira'l ara mateix!

ko.title: 비스트 게임 | 2화(풀영상)
ko.description:
어떻게 아마존을 잘 설득해서 첫 3개 에피소드를 여기에 올릴 수 있게 했는데... 나머지는 Prime Video에서만 볼 수 있어요. 지금 바로 시청하세요! https://unfur.ly/BeastGames

비스트게임 크레딧 : https://youtu.be/5xSirFgIPOM

kn.title: ನನ್ನ ನಗರದಲ್ಲಿ 500 ಜನರು ಸಿಕ್ಕಿಬಿದ್ದಿದ್ದಾರೆ
kn.description:
https://youtu.be/3uKsaGRK3yw

ಉಳಿದ 500 ಸ್ಪರ್ಧಿಗಳು ನಾನು ಮೊದಲಿನಿಂದ ನಿರ್ಮಿಸಿದ ಬೃಹತ್ ನಗರದಲ್ಲಿ ಉಳಿಯಲು ಹೋರಾಡಬೇಕು (ತಮಾಷೆಯಲ್ಲ).  ಧಾರಾವಾಹಿಯ ಅಂತ್ಯವು ದೂರದರ್ಶನದ ಇತಿಹಾಸದಲ್ಲಿ ಇದುವರೆಗೆ ಸಂಭವಿಸಿದ ಅತ್ಯಂತ ಅಸಾಮಾನ್ಯ ಸಂಗತಿಯಾಗಿದೆ.   ಇದೀಗ ಅದನ್ನು ವೀಕ್ಷಿಸಿ!

hi.title: बीस्ट गेम्ज़| एपिसोड  2 (फुल एपिसोड )
hi.description:
मैंने किसी तरह Amazon को मनाया कि मैं पहले 3 एपिसोड यहाँ पोस्ट कर सकूँ... लेकिन बाकी सिर्फ़ Prime Video पर हैं! अभी देखें! 
https://unfur.ly/BeastGames

बीस्ट गेम्ज़ क्रेडिट्स: https://youtu.be/5xSirFgIPOM

id.title: Beast Games | Episode 2 (Episode Lengkap)
id.description:
Aku meminta Amazon untuk mengizinkan aku mengupload 3 episode pertama di sini..... tapi sisanya HANYA ada di Prime Video. Ayo tonton sekarang!
https://unfur.ly/BeastGames

Beast Games Credits: https://youtu.be/5xSirFgIPOM

cs.title: 500 lidí uvízlo v mém městě
cs.description: Zbývajících 500 účastníků musí bojovat o své místo v tomto OBROVSKÉM městě, které jsem postavil úplně od základů (a to vážně nepřeháním). Konec tohoto dílu je možná tou nejšílenější událostí v historii televizních pořadů. Sledujte už teď!

fil.title: 500 Katao Ang Na-trap Sa Aking Lungsod
fil.description:
https://youtu.be/3uKsaGRK3yw

Ang natitirang 500 kalahok ay kailangang lumaban para manatili sa NAPAKALAKING lungsod na ako mismo ang gumawa mula sa wala (hindi ako nagbibiro). Ang pagtatapos ng episode na ito ay maaaring ang pinakamalupit na nangyari sa kasaysayan ng telebisyon. Panoorin mo na ngayon!

uk.title: 500 людей опинилися в моєму місті
uk.description:
https://youtu.be/3uKsaGRK3yw

Решта 500 учасників повинні боротися за те, щоб залишитися в ВЕЛИЧЕЗНОМУ місті, яке я побудував з нуля (не жартую). Кінець епізоду може бути найбожевільнішим, що коли-небудь траплялося в історії телебачення. Дивіться шоу прямо зараз!

vi.title: Beast Games | Tập 2 (Full)
vi.description:
Tôi đã thuyết phục được Amazon để đăng 3 tập đầu tại đây… nhưng các tập còn lại chỉ chiếu ĐỘC QUYỀN trên Prime Video. Xem ngay! https://unfur.ly/BeastGames 

Credit Beast Games: https://youtu.be/5xSirFgIPOM

gu.title: ૫૦૦ લોકો મારા શહેરમાં ફસાયા છે
gu.description:
https://youtu.be/3uKsaGRK3yw

બાકીના ૫00 કોન્ટેસ્ટેન્ટસને,
 મેં મારા પોતાના હાથથી બનાવેલા  (મજાક નહીં) વિશાળ શહેરમાં રહેવા માટે લડવું પડશે. એપિસોડનો અંત ટેલિવિઝનના ઇતિહાસમાં સૌથી ક્રેઝી વસ્તુ હોઈ શકે છે.તો હમણાં જ જુઓ!

sr.title: 500 ljudi je zarobljeno u mom gradu
sr.description:
https://youtu.be/3uKsaGRK3yw

Preostalih 500 takmičara moraju da se bore da bi ostali u OGROMNOM gradu koji sam napravio iz temelja (bez šale). Kraj epizode ​​je možda najluđa stvar koja se ikada dogodila u istoriji televizije.  Gledajte odmah!

tr.title: Beast Games | Bölüm 2 (Tam Bölüm)
tr.description:
Bir şekilde Amazon'u ilk 3 bölümü buraya koymama izin vermeye ikna ettim... ama geri kalanı SADECE Prime Video'da. Hemen gidip izleyin! https://unfur.ly/BeastGames

Beast Games Katkıda Bulunanlar: https://youtu.be/5xSirFgIPOM

pt.title: Beast Games | Episódio 2 (Episódio completo)
pt.description:
De algum jeito eu convenci a Amazon a deixar eu postar os primeiros três episódios aqui... mas o restante está SOMENTE no Prime Video.
https://unfur.ly/BeastGames

Créditos do Beast Games: https://youtu.be/5xSirFgIPOM

ms.title: 500 Orang Terkurung Dalam Bandar Saya
ms.description:
https://unfur.ly/BeastGames

500 peserta yang tinggal perlu bersaing untuk kekal di bandar BESAR yang saya bina dari kosong (bukan gurauan). Pengakhiran episod ini mungkin perkara paling gila yang pernah berlaku dalam sejarah televisyen. Tonton sekarang!

el.title: 500 άτομα παγιδεύονται στην πόλη μου
el.description:
https://youtu.be/3uKsaGRK3yw

Οι 500 εναπομείναντες διαγωνιζόμενοι πρέπει να τα δώσουν όλα για να μείνουν στην ΤΕΡΑΣΤΙΑ πόλη που έχτισα από το μηδέν (δεν κάνω πλάκα). Το τέλος του επεισοδίου ίσως είναι ό,τι πιο τρελό έχει συμβεί ποτέ στην ιστορία της τηλεόρασης. Δείτε το τώρα!

hu.title: 500 összezárt ember a városomban
hu.description:
https://youtu.be/3uKsaGRK3yw

A maradék 500 versenyzőnek meg kell küzdenie azért, hogy a HATALMAS városban maradhasson, amit a semmiből építettem fel. (Nem viccelek.) Az epizód végén a vetélkedők történetének talán legőrültebb eseménye bontakozik ki. Nézd meg most azonnal!

th.title: Beast Games บีสต์เกมส์ | ตอนที่ 2 (ตอนเต็ม)
th.description:
ผมได้คุยกับ Amazon เพื่อให้ผมโพสต์ 3 ตอนแรกที่นี่ได้สำเร็จ แต่ที่เหลือมีให้รับชมได้เฉพาะบน Prime Video เท่านั้น ไปกันดูเลยตอนนี้! https://unfur.ly/BeastGames

Beast Games (บีสต์เกมส์) เครดิต: https://youtu.be/5xSirFgIPOM

it.title: Beast Games | Episodio 2 (Puntata completa)
it.description:
Sono riuscito a convincere Amazon a farmi postare le prime 3 puntate qui... ma il resto è SOLO su Prime Video. Vai a guardarlo ora! https://unfur.ly/BeastGames

Crediti Beast Games: https://youtu.be/5xSirFgIPOM

mr.title: बीस्ट गेम्स | भाग २ (पूर्ण भाग)
mr.description:
मी कसे तरी Amazon ला पहिले ३ एपिसोड इथे पोस्ट करण्याची परवानगी देण्यास सांगितले... पण बाकीचे फक्त प्राइम व्हिडिओवर आहेत. आताच पहा! https://unfur.ly/BeastGames 

बीस्ट गेम्स क्रेडिट्स: https://youtu.be/5xSirFgIPOM

sv.title: 500 personer fångade i min stad
sv.description:
https://youtu.be/3uKsaGRK3yw

De återstående 500 tävlande måste kämpa för att stanna kvar i den ENORMA staden jag byggde från grunden (ingen skämt). Slutet på avsnittet kan vara det galnaste som någonsin hänt i TV-historien. Titta på det nu!

snippet.description:
In the 1st ODI, Sri Lanka won the toss and elected to bat first. The home side put a hard-fought 214 runs on the board with Asalanka scoring a great hundred. Australia however had a tough chase as they became all out for just 165 runs in 33.5 overs. Sri Lanka won by 49 runs in the end.

snippet.title: HIGHLIGHTS Man City 2-3 Real Madrid | Haaland (2), Mbappe, Diaz & Bellingham Goals
snippet.description:
City face a tough task to progress in the Champions League after losing the first play-off leg 3-2 to Real Madrid.

Erling Haaland twice put the Blues ahead in a thrilling encounter, but the Spanish side hit back each time, before snatching victory with almost the final kick of the game.

It leaves City needing to win by at least a goal in the second leg to at least level the aggregate scores and have any chance of progressing after a heart-breaking final seven minutes.

kn.title: ಸಾವಿರಾರು ಜನರು $5,000,000 ಹಣಕ್ಕಾಗಿ ಹೋರಾಡುತ್ತಿದ್ದರು
kn.description:
https://youtu.be/Yv8xg0FMDXw

ನಾನು $5,000,000 ಗಾಗಿ ಹೋರಾಡಲು 1,000 ಜನರನ್ನು ಒಟ್ಟುಗೂಡಿಸಿದೆ, ಇದು ಟಿವಿ ಇತಿಹಾಸದಲ್ಲಿ ಅತಿ ದೊಡ್ಡ ನಗದು ಬಹುಮಾನವಾಗಿದೆ!  ನೀವು ಇದನ್ನು ಇನ್ನೂ ಏಕೆ ಓದುತ್ತಿದ್ದೀರಿ ಎಂದು ನನಗೆ ತಿಳಿದಿಲ್ಲ, ಇದೀಗ ಅದನ್ನು ವೀಕ್ಷಿಸಿ!  ಇನ್ನು ಸ್ಪಾಯ್ಲರ್‌ಗಳಿಲ್ಲ.

fil.description:
https://youtu.be/Yv8xg0FMDXw

https://youtu.be/Yv8xg0FMDXw

הזכייה הכי גדולה בתולדות הטלוויזיה!

כנסו לצפות ממש עכשיו! מספיק עם הספויילרים.

uk.title: 1,000 учасників змагаються за приз у $ 5,000,000

 માટે લડવા ૧,૦૦૦ લોકોને ભેગા કર્યા, જે ટીવીના ઇતિહાસમાં સૌથી મોટું રોકડ પુરસ્કાર છે! મને ખબર નથી કે તમે હજી પણ આ કેમ વાંચી રહ્યાં છો, હમણાં જ તેને જુઓ! નો મોરે સ્પોઈલર્સ.

About MaaTri Media 

MaaTri, represents the most beautiful relationship between a mother and a daughter - Nisha Topwal & Anantya Anand aka. MyMissAnand. MaaTri is formed through a combination of two Hindi words - Maa (Mother) and PuTri (daughter) that brings forth energy, enthusiasm and determination to spread positive vibes through their outstanding content. Their content revolves around fashion, food, comedy, parenting, travel, glimpse of their family and simple day-to-day activities that both enjoy doing together. 
The duo captures a contemporary lifestyle of entrepreneur and food blogger mom and a teenage daughter and a social media influencer and shows how they both manage their work, school and personal life - simple pleasure of growing together, through engaging videos and fun visuals. Every post is curated and designed to make the audience laugh, learn, smile and entertain.

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :

Sunn Mera Dil Digitally Presented by LUX - Happilac Paints and Ujooba Beauty Cream

7th Sky Entertainment’s highly anticipated mega signature project, Sunn Mere Dil, is the most awaited drama serial. The mega drama boasts a star-studded cast led by Wahaj Ali and Maya Ali. Written by the renowned Khalil Ur Rehman Qamar and directed by the acclaimed Haseeb Hasan, Sunn Mere Dil promises to be a one-of-a-kind drama.

Sunn Mere Dil is a tale in which love finds a new meaning, where one person’s devotion quietly flourishes, often unnoticed. Their heart beats for someone who may never truly understand the depth of their feelings. Yet, in their silent sacrifices, they realize that true love is not about
possession but about selflessness.

Every unspoken gesture and unseen act of kindness brings them fulfillment, as they put their beloved’s happiness above their own, showing that love is not just about being together, it’s about redefining happiness, even at the expense of their contentment.

🎬 Movie Plot 🎬
Sankranthiki Vasthunam is the Hattrick film under the collaboration of Victory #venkateshdaggubati, Hit Machine Director #AnilRavipudi and Blockbuster Producers Dilraju and Shirish. snippet.title: How To Train Your Dragon | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
How To Train Your Dragon - In Theaters June 13

From three-time Oscar® nominee and Golden Globe winner Dean DeBlois, the creative visionary behind DreamWorks Animation’s acclaimed How to Train Your Dragon trilogy, comes a stunning live-action reimagining of the film that launched the beloved franchise. 

On the rugged isle of Berk, where Vikings and dragons have been bitter enemies for generations, Hiccup (Mason Thames; The Black Phone, For All Mankind) stands apart. The inventive yet overlooked son of Chief Stoick the Vast (Gerard Butler, reprising his voice role from the animated franchise), Hiccup defies centuries of tradition when he befriends Toothless, a feared Night Fury dragon. Their unlikely bond reveals the true nature of dragons, challenging the very foundations of Viking society. 

With the fierce and ambitious Astrid (BAFTA nominee Nico Parker; Dumbo, The Last of Us) and the village’s quirky blacksmith Gobber (Nick Frost; Snow White and the Huntsman, Shaun of the Dead) by his side, Hiccup confronts a world torn by fear and misunderstanding. 

As an ancient threat emerges, endangering both Vikings and dragons, Hiccup’s friendship with Toothless becomes the key to forging a new future. Together, they must navigate the delicate path toward peace, soaring beyond the boundaries of their worlds and redefining what it means to be a hero and a leader. 

The film also stars Julian Dennison (Deadpool 2), Gabriel Howell (Bodies), Bronwyn James (Wicked), Harry Trevaldwyn (Smothered), Ruth Codd (The Midnight Club), BAFTA nominee Peter Serafinowicz (Guardians of the Galaxy) and Murray McArthur (Game of Thrones).
How to Train Your Dragon is written, produced and directed by DeBlois. It is also produced by three-time Oscar® nominee Marc Platt (Wicked, La La Land) and Emmy winner Adam Siegel (Drive, 2 Guns). How To Train Your Dragon is part of the Filmed For IMAX® Program, which offers filmmakers IMAX® technology to help them deliver the most immersive movie experience to audiences around the world. 

Inspired by Cressida Cowell’s New York Times bestselling book series, DreamWorks Animation’s How to Train Your Dragon franchise has captivated global audiences, earning four Academy Award® nominations and grossing more than $1.6 billion at the global box-office. Now, through cutting-edge visual effects, DeBlois transforms his beloved animated saga into a breathtaking live-action spectacle, bringing the epic adventures of Hiccup and Toothless to life with jaw-dropping realism as they discover the true meaning of friendship, courage and destiny.

snippet.title: Jetha ने Daya के साथ किया खुलकर Romance | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Valentine Day Special
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to Sony Pal: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCw7xjxzbMwgBSmbeYwqYRMg

Jethalal is trying to romance his wife but Champaklal's presence prevents him from doing so. He also tells Jethalal to take care of his health and scolds him about his lifestyle. Stay tuned to find out more.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episode No - 499
Produced By -  Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sonypal #Latest #tmkoc #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2025 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLfyXOEyr93G258PCh3zUzDHfYjQP_zP2d

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: NEW! Ep 4320 - Bhavishyvani Sun Ghabra Gaya Popatlal?! | Taarak Mehta ka Ooltah Chashmah
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Sachin Shroff / Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta

Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide

Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani / Khushi Mali as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi

snippet.title: Strawberry Shortcake Recipe in Tamil
snippet.description:
In this video, we will see how to make Strawberry Shortcake, a classic dessert that’s light, fluffy, and bursting with fresh strawberry flavor! This homemade strawberry shortcake recipe features soft, buttery shortcakes layered with sweet, juicy strawberries and topped with fluffy whipped cream, making it the perfect treat for any occasion. Whether you're looking for a delicious summer dessert, a special birthday treat, or just something sweet to enjoy with your family, this easy strawberry shortcake recipe is a must-try! The combination of tender cake, fresh fruit, and rich cream creates a delightful balance of flavors and textures that’s hard to resist.
#strawberryshortcake #strawberrycake 

Friends, do try this strawberry shortcake recipe at home and enjoy this bakery-style treat with your loved ones. Don’t forget to share your feedback in the comments below. All the best and happy cooking!

Ingredients for the sheet cake:
1/2 cup Butter at room temperature (100g)
3/4 cup Sugar (150g)
2 eggs
2 tsp Vanilla extract
1 cup Maida
1 tsp baking powder
1/4 tsp Salt
1/3 cup Milk
Bake at 350F/175C for 12 -14 min (13*9 inch pan)

For Strawberry jam:
350g strawberry
1/4 cup Sugar
pinch of Salt
few drops of Lemon juice

For simple sugar syrup:
1/4 cup Water
1/4 cup Sugar

For Cream:
3/4 cup whipping cream
3-4 tbsp Sugar 
(i have used 1cup cream i this video, we only need 3/4 cup cream, use 3 tbsp Sugar)

snippet.description:
झोलझाल कॉमेडी - Best Comedy Scenes | राजपाल यादव और परेश रावल की लोटपोट कॉमेडी | Akshay Kumar Comedy
#shemaroocomedy #rajpalyadav #pareshrawal 

Watch the hilarious Jhojhaal Comedy featuring Rajpal Yadav, Paresh Rawal, and Mukesh Tiwari. Get ready to laugh out loud with this comedy special!

"Sachin Tichkule is an ambitious contractor who faces opposition from everyone, both at home and at work. But he continues to struggle while his family members continue to pocket ill-gained money.
Movie - Khatta Meetha(2010)
Star Cast: Akshay Kumar, Trisha Krishnan, Johny Lever , Rajpal Yadav, Asrani, Kulbhushan Kharbanda, Aruna Irani, Urvashi Sharma, Milind Gunaji
Director - Priyadarshan

सचिन टिचकुले एक महत्वाकांक्षी ठेकेदार है जिसे घर और कार्यस्थल दोनों जगह हर किसी के विरोध का सामना करना पड़ता है। लेकिन वह संघर्ष करना जारी रखता है जबकि उसके परिवार के सदस्य गलत तरीके से कमाए गए पैसे को हड़पने में लगे रहते हैं।
मूवी - खट्टा मीठा (2010)
स्टार कास्ट: अक्षय कुमार, तृषा कृष्णन, जॉनी लीवर, राजपाल यादव, असरानी, ​​कुलभूषण खरबंदा, अरुणा ईरानी, ​​उर्वशी शर्मा, मिलिंद गुणाजी
निर्देशक - प्रियदर्शन

The lives of Raju, Shyam and Baburao change completely when they get cheated by a fraudster. Now, they must find another way to repay the loan they took from a dreaded gangster.

Movie - Phir Hera Pheri (2006)
Star Cast - Akshay Kumar, Sunil Shetty, Paresh Rawal, Bipasha Basu, Rimi, Johny Lever
Director - Neeraj Vora
Producer - Firoz A. Nadiadwala

राजू, श्याम और बाबूराव का जीवन पूरी तरह से बदल जाता है जब उन्हें एक धोखेबाज द्वारा धोखा दिया जाता है। अब, उन्हें एक खूंखार गैंगस्टर से लिए गए कर्ज को चुकाने का दूसरा तरीका खोजना होगा।

फिल्म - फिर हेरा फेरी (2006)
स्टार कास्ट - अक्षय कुमार, सुनील शेट्टी, परेश रावल, बिपाशा बसु, रिमी, जॉनी लीवर

Hoping to boost his marriage prospects, Popatlal begins feeding pigeons by scattering grains on Bhide’s Sakharam. Will Bhide allow it?

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.
